videos.headline: Pitt's Pickett fires touchdown to Addison
videos.description: Pittsburgh finishes a 12-play, 60-yard drive with a Kenny Pickett touchdown strike to Jordan Addison.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt's Pickett fires touchdown to Addison) 2020/9/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hawkins houses 75-yard run for Louisville
videos.description: Javian Hawkins answers Pittsburgh's first-quarter score with a 75-yard touchdown run for Louisville.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hawkins houses 75-yard run for Louisville) 2020/9/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Louisville's Cunningham flings TD to Atwell
videos.description: The Cardinals take their first lead of the game over Pittsburgh on Malik Cunningham's 21-yard touchdown to Tutu Atwell.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Louisville's Cunningham flings TD to Atwell) 2020/9/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pitt's Mack shows incredible awareness on fourth-down score
videos.description: Louisville defenders nearly bring Taysir Mack to the ground, but Mack plays on and chugs 40 yards to the end zone for a Pittsburgh touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt's Mack shows incredible awareness on fourth-down score) 2020/9/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pitt breaks out mini hoop in electric turnover celebration
videos.description: Marquis Williams intercepts Louisville QB Malik Cunningham, then Williams joins his Pittsburgh teammates with a synchronized dunk celebration.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt breaks out mini hoop in electric turnover celebration) 2020/9/26 ESHEET
